app_instructions:
HTML/JS App Structure:
    - Dropdown: Commodity (from uniques.commodities)
    - Slider: Farm Size (0.1-10 acres)
    - Input: Investment (₹0-10L)
    - Button: Calculate → Show min/avg/max revenue/profit/ROI table
    - Predict Mode: Hide commodity → Auto-best crop
    - Charts: Bar for revenue ranges using Chart.js
    Data 100% complete from mandi file.
